    <h3>No attributes with <code>component</code> helper</h3>

    <h4>Problem</h4>
    With angle-brackets, there are now attributes and arguments that can be passed in to a component. The <code>component</code>
    helper uses the attribute syntax for arguments and is itself incapable of providing support for this.

    <h4>Solution</h4>
    A solution is on the horizon that will pretty much look like the workaround we have to use for now.

    <h4>Workaround</h4>
    Use <a href="https://github.com/mmun/ember-component-attributes"><code>ember-component-attributes</code></a> addon. It will provide
    a <code>html-attributes</code> helper for usage inside <code>component</code> helper.
